You guys stay inside.

268
00:17:09,737 --> 00:17:11,405
Amando is outside.

269
00:17:11,905 --> 00:17:13,157
He killed Bill too.

270
00:17:13,866 --> 00:17:14,908
What?

271
00:17:14,992 --> 00:17:16,618
My God…

272
00:17:16,702 --> 00:17:18,078
We were about to get out.

273
00:17:18,162 --> 00:17:20,039
We thought Amando was inside.

274
00:17:20,122 --> 00:17:22,124
No, Auntie Mercy. Please.

275
00:17:22,624 --> 00:17:25,169
He's still outside, so stay inside.

276
00:17:25,252 --> 00:17:27,254
Find a place to hide there.

277
00:17:27,838 --> 00:17:29,590
Thank you for warning us.

278
00:17:30,174 --> 00:17:31,884
Sam, please be careful.

279
00:17:31,967 --> 00:17:33,260
Keep our baby safe.

280
00:17:33,886 --> 00:17:36,305
Mother, let's go
to the staff room. Come on.

281
00:17:36,889 --> 00:17:37,848
Sam.

282
00:17:39,016 --> 00:17:40,434
Give me Paco's child.

283
00:17:42,144 --> 00:17:43,604
Don't come near us.

284
00:17:46,065 --> 00:17:47,107
Don't come near.

285
00:17:51,487 --> 00:17:54,490
Aurora, stop bothering
Sam and my grandson.

286
00:17:54,573 --> 00:17:58,243
Amando might come back and kill us all.

287
00:17:59,912 --> 00:18:00,746
Aurora.

288
00:18:00,829 --> 00:18:02,122
Don't come any closer.

289
00:18:03,373 --> 00:18:06,376
No, don't come any closer.
Don't come any closer.

290
00:18:09,505 --> 00:18:11,715
Aurora, Sam. What the hell is happening?

291
00:18:12,299 --> 00:18:14,343
Hide from Amando.

292
00:18:17,429 --> 00:18:18,639
Amando?

293
00:18:19,139 --> 00:18:20,474
Stay there.

294
00:18:20,557 --> 00:18:21,725
Oh, my God.

295
00:18:23,977 --> 00:18:25,062
Sam,

296
00:18:25,771 --> 00:18:27,064
run.

297
00:18:28,565 --> 00:18:32,861
Sam, I'm not the killer. Believe me.

298
00:18:39,743 --> 00:18:41,120
You are wet…

299
00:18:41,912 --> 00:18:42,788
You…

300
00:18:43,288 --> 00:18:44,289
You killed Bill.

301
00:18:45,499 --> 00:18:49,169
Yes, I went out
to find you and protect you.

302
00:18:49,253 --> 00:18:52,131
But, I saw Bill fighting
with the killer for the gun.

303
00:18:52,214 --> 00:18:54,174
That's why I came back here.

304
00:18:54,258 --> 00:18:55,801
I didn't kill him.

305
00:18:55,884 --> 00:18:57,010
Liar.

306
00:19:00,514 --> 00:19:01,682
You're the Palacios killer.

307
00:19:08,021 --> 00:19:12,693
You killed my guard, Galvan's guard,
the roaming guard, Ando.

308
00:19:12,776 --> 00:19:14,736
And now, Bill?

309
00:19:14,820 --> 00:19:17,948
Stay back or I'll shoot you, Amando.

310
00:19:18,657 --> 00:19:22,411
Aurora, you know I can't kill anyone.

311
00:19:23,829 --> 00:19:26,165
I'm not the Palacios killer.

312
00:19:26,248 --> 00:19:29,501
Put down the gun. Come with me.

313
00:19:29,585 --> 00:19:30,878
I'll protect you.

314
00:19:30,961 --> 00:19:32,462
I said stay back.

315
00:19:34,381 --> 00:19:37,926
Aurora put down the gun.
Come with me, and protect--

316
00:19:48,228 --> 00:19:49,646
Okay, Aurora,

317
00:19:50,397 --> 00:19:51,523
if you don't want to.

318
00:19:52,649 --> 00:19:53,817
Just come with me.

319
00:19:53,901 --> 00:19:55,694
I'll take you to a safe place

320
00:19:55,777 --> 00:19:59,698
where your son won't be involved
in the Palacios killer's revenge, Sam.

321
00:20:00,282 --> 00:20:02,743
Stop your madness, Amando.

322
00:20:05,871 --> 00:20:07,789
Sam, listen.

323
00:20:07,873 --> 00:20:10,500
I won't let anything bad happen to you,

324
00:20:11,168 --> 00:20:12,377
especially to your child…

325
00:20:13,629 --> 00:20:15,172
because you're my family.

326
00:20:15,881 --> 00:20:17,549
Paco is my son.

327
00:20:17,633 --> 00:20:19,426
I'm his real father.

328
00:20:20,010 --> 00:20:21,970
Don't believe him, Sam.

329
00:20:23,805 --> 00:20:26,433
Sam, what I said is true.

330
00:20:27,226 --> 00:20:29,186
Something happened to Aurora and me.

331
00:20:29,269 --> 00:20:30,229
Paco is my child.

332
00:20:30,312 --> 00:20:32,814
That's enough. Stop it, Amando.

333
00:20:33,857 --> 00:20:35,525
That child is my flesh and blood.

334
00:20:36,443 --> 00:20:38,320
That's why I would never hurt him.

335
00:20:40,405 --> 00:20:41,281
Sam…

336
00:20:43,158 --> 00:20:44,534
Believe me.

337
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:50,040
Can I look at Paco's child?

338
00:20:50,123 --> 00:20:51,917
Do you want to hold him?

339
00:20:55,170 --> 00:20:56,797
He looks like Paco.

340
00:20:57,798 --> 00:20:58,674
Is it true?

341
00:21:00,175 --> 00:21:01,551
Is it true?

342
00:21:01,635 --> 00:21:02,761
You…

343
00:21:03,428 --> 00:21:04,972
Are you Paco's father?

344
00:21:09,685 --> 00:21:12,145
Dad, is it true what Amando said,

345
00:21:13,146 --> 00:21:15,899
that he and Auntie Aurora had an affair?

346
00:21:15,983 --> 00:21:18,151
They are not in a relationship.

347
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:23,657
They just said something happened to them.

348
00:21:26,702 --> 00:21:27,911
In that case,

349
00:21:29,705 --> 00:21:31,999
Amando is Paco's father

350
00:21:32,708 --> 00:21:35,002
Sam's baby is his grandson.

351
00:21:38,755 --> 00:21:41,258
This revelation is crazy.

352
00:21:42,175 --> 00:21:47,222
Something happened to Amando
and Ma'am Aurora, is that right?

353
00:21:57,065 --> 00:21:58,775
Is it true, Mom Aurora?

354
00:22:00,944 --> 00:22:02,571
Is my son his grandson?

355
00:22:05,032 --> 00:22:06,116
What, Aurora?

356
00:22:06,950 --> 00:22:08,618
Why aren't you talking?

357
00:22:09,661 --> 00:22:11,538
Tell them the truth,

358
00:22:12,039 --> 00:22:13,540
that I'm Paco's father.

359
00:22:14,124 --> 00:22:16,418
It's all in your head, Amando.

360
00:22:17,586 --> 00:22:21,214
No matter what,
Aurora Palacios would never fall

361
00:22:21,298 --> 00:22:23,633
for a poor guy like you.

362
00:22:25,302 --> 00:22:27,220
You really have no shame, Aurora.

363
00:22:27,804 --> 00:22:29,347
Until the end,

364
00:22:29,890 --> 00:22:31,933
all that comes out of your mouth is lies.

365
00:22:32,017 --> 00:22:34,603
I'm not lying.

366
00:22:34,686 --> 00:22:38,732
Amando, you're too delusional,
too ambitious.

367
00:22:39,441 --> 00:22:41,443
You're an animal. Animal.

368
00:22:48,158 --> 00:22:50,744
Good, Aurora. It's about time.

369
00:22:50,827 --> 00:22:53,455
Oh, my God… Oh, my God…

370
00:22:54,623 --> 00:22:57,167
- Sis… who died?
- Oh, my God.

371
00:22:57,876 --> 00:22:59,336
Sis, are you okay?

372
00:23:00,378 --> 00:23:02,130
<i>Let that be your warning, Amando.</i>

373
00:23:02,714 --> 00:23:06,510
If you still don't stop your madness,
I will really kill you.

374
00:23:08,553 --> 00:23:10,472
You can kill me, Aurora,

375
00:23:11,765 --> 00:23:14,101
but you can't kill the truth

376
00:23:15,227 --> 00:23:16,728
that Paco is my son,

377
00:23:17,854 --> 00:23:19,397
and I'm the grandfather of Sam's son.

378
00:23:20,148 --> 00:23:23,443
And I will do everything
to save them from your madness.

379
00:23:23,527 --> 00:23:24,861
That's enough.

380
00:23:24,945 --> 00:23:27,405
That's enough, Amando.
That's enough, please.

381
00:23:28,573 --> 00:23:31,618
You can't say anything
that will change my mind.

382
00:23:31,701 --> 00:23:33,912
I won't go with either of you

383
00:23:33,995 --> 00:23:36,123
because I don't trust either of you.

384
00:23:37,833 --> 00:23:39,376
Go away.

385
00:23:40,168 --> 00:23:41,837
Go away.

386
00:23:45,090 --> 00:23:45,924
Go, Aurora.

387
00:23:46,007 --> 00:23:51,346
Shoot that killer in the head
so that our problems will stop.

388
00:23:53,598 --> 00:23:56,351
Do you really think
Amando is the Palacios killer?

389
00:23:57,102 --> 00:24:01,481
George, if not him, who?

390
00:24:05,318 --> 00:24:07,571
Sam, Auntie Aurora. Where are you?

391
00:24:08,155 --> 00:24:09,281
What's the gunshot we heard?

392
00:24:09,865 --> 00:24:11,408
Ma'am Aurora, where are you?

393
00:24:12,868 --> 00:24:15,996
Sam, be careful.

394
00:24:16,580 --> 00:24:17,998
Take care of my grandson.

395
00:24:25,964 --> 00:24:27,215
Mother.

396
00:24:33,930 --> 00:24:35,640
What was that gunshot we heard?

397
00:24:36,725 --> 00:24:39,895
Amando came back here.
He tried to take us,

398
00:24:39,978 --> 00:24:41,521
but Aurora shot him.

399
00:24:42,397 --> 00:24:44,065
- Where is he?
- He's gone.

400
00:24:44,149 --> 00:24:46,234
Aurora let him escape.

401
00:24:46,318 --> 00:24:47,319
What?

402
00:24:47,402 --> 00:24:50,155
Ma'am Aurora, why did you
let Sir Amando escape?

403
00:24:50,238 --> 00:24:53,783
Auntie, all of our lives are
at stake here,

404
00:24:53,867 --> 00:24:55,869
and you let him escape?

405
00:24:57,412 --> 00:24:58,663
<i>Sam, are you okay?</i>

406
00:24:59,706 --> 00:25:02,125
<i>We heard what Amando said.</i>

407
00:25:04,127 --> 00:25:05,128
Actually…

408
00:25:06,087 --> 00:25:07,839
Dad confirmed that

409
00:25:08,423 --> 00:25:10,884
something happened to Aunt Aurora
and Amando, but…

410
00:25:11,551 --> 00:25:14,054
it was a mistake on Auntie Aurora's part.

411
00:25:17,265 --> 00:25:21,561
But, I think
Amando really loves Mom Aurora.

412
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:24,481
And Auntie Aurora used that fact.

413
00:25:26,066 --> 00:25:30,570
She did that so she could
get everything she wanted,

414
00:25:31,363 --> 00:25:34,908
so that all her plans could happen
through Amando.

415
00:25:34,991 --> 00:25:36,660
Do you think, sis…

416
00:25:37,994 --> 00:25:42,499
she used Amando's love
to make him do whatever she wanted,

417
00:25:43,166 --> 00:25:46,461
to get rid of all the people
she didn't want in her life…

418
00:25:48,546 --> 00:25:49,965
like Dad?

419
00:25:52,717 --> 00:25:54,552
Dad, what are you doing?

420
00:25:54,636 --> 00:25:57,472
I don't want to give in to the fear
caused by that Amando anymore.

421
00:25:58,306 --> 00:26:02,852
I need to confront him
so his threats to our family can stop.

422
00:26:11,236 --> 00:26:13,613
Don't ever touch my son.

423
00:26:18,326 --> 00:26:20,036
Mother, let's get out of here.

424
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:21,579
Jericho, I'll go crazy here.

425
00:26:21,663 --> 00:26:23,039
We have to leave…

426
00:26:23,123 --> 00:26:25,041
before Amando comes back.

427
00:26:25,125 --> 00:26:27,085
Sam, that's a dangerous idea.

428
00:26:27,168 --> 00:26:30,005
It's still dark outside
and the rain hasn't stopped yet.

429
00:26:31,631 --> 00:26:33,466
We have a gun.

430
00:26:34,301 --> 00:26:37,637
But, we don't know where Amando is
and if he's with anyone else.

431
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:40,515
Jericho is right, Ma'am Sam.

432
00:26:40,598 --> 00:26:43,893
It's better if we stay inside for now.
At least until he is stopped.

433
00:26:44,811 --> 00:26:47,147
It's risky, we might get caught
in the dark.

434
00:26:48,315 --> 00:26:49,357
Let's go to the basement.

435
00:26:49,941 --> 00:26:51,484
No, not there. Not in the basement.

436
00:26:51,568 --> 00:26:54,070
We won't be heard there.
We won't be seen there.

437
00:26:56,990 --> 00:26:59,826
In the study…
Let's go to the study. Come on.

438
00:26:59,909 --> 00:27:01,328
- This way.
- Let's go.

439
00:27:09,294 --> 00:27:12,672
And so I can get revenge
for poisoning Basil.

440
00:27:13,256 --> 00:27:17,427
But, how sure are you
that Amando poisoned Basil?

441
00:27:18,094 --> 00:27:20,597
Because Paco and Basil were at odds.

442
00:27:21,598 --> 00:27:26,144
That's probably why he used
to think Basil pushed Paco.

443
00:27:26,644 --> 00:27:29,147
That's why he's taking revenge.
He's taking revenge on all of us.

444
00:27:30,482 --> 00:27:31,858
He's losing his mind.

445
00:27:31,941 --> 00:27:35,195
Look. He stabbed me.

446
00:27:36,029 --> 00:27:40,158
He's on a killing spree.
That's why we're locked up here now.

447
00:27:40,241 --> 00:27:41,076
Dad…

448
00:27:42,243 --> 00:27:46,539
I also want to make Amando pay
if he killed my husband,

449
00:27:47,248 --> 00:27:50,418
but you confronting him is dangerous.

450
00:27:50,502 --> 00:27:53,254
Yes, Sir Galvan. The children are right.

451
00:27:53,338 --> 00:27:56,883
How can you be sure
that Amando acted alone

452
00:27:56,966 --> 00:27:58,843
and had no accomplices?

453
00:27:58,927 --> 00:28:01,179
I don't care how many there are.

454
00:28:01,262 --> 00:28:02,806
I have a gun.

455
00:28:02,889 --> 00:28:04,808
I'm ready to kill them.

456
00:28:04,891 --> 00:28:09,187
The important thing is
that Amando's evil ways must stop.

457
00:28:10,230 --> 00:28:11,731
But, Dad. Dad, please.

458
00:28:12,565 --> 00:28:14,067
I'm scared.

459
00:28:14,901 --> 00:28:16,486
I already lost Mommy.

460
00:28:23,993 --> 00:28:26,079
You won't catch me alive.

461
00:28:27,330 --> 00:28:30,667
We'll die first before you catch me.

462
00:28:34,337 --> 00:28:35,839
Miss Trano…

463
00:28:35,922 --> 00:28:37,173
Surrender.

464
00:28:52,772 --> 00:28:54,983
Sir, we recovered the car earlier.

465
00:28:55,650 --> 00:28:58,361
We had a hard time
because the river was too deep.

466
00:28:59,070 --> 00:29:00,488
How about Mommy?

467
00:29:00,572 --> 00:29:02,866
Where is she? Where did you take her?

468
00:29:02,949 --> 00:29:05,785
Sofia, no body was recovered from the car.

469
00:29:05,869 --> 00:29:08,997
She may have slipped through
the windshield and was swept away.

470
00:29:09,497 --> 00:29:12,459
Then go find her.
What are you doing? Find her.

471
00:29:12,542 --> 00:29:15,253
She might be in desperate need
of help right now.

472
00:29:16,004 --> 00:29:17,714
We're doing everything we can, Sofia.

473
00:29:17,797 --> 00:29:20,216
But, your mom's car is a total wreck.

474
00:29:24,012 --> 00:29:26,598
I don't want to lose you

475
00:29:27,432 --> 00:29:30,977
just because some crazy man is
trying to massacre our family.

476
00:29:31,060 --> 00:29:32,228
Dad…

477
00:29:34,105 --> 00:29:35,315
Don't worry, Sofia.

478
00:29:36,191 --> 00:29:37,776
You won't lose Daddy.

479
00:29:38,485 --> 00:29:39,986
I'll be very careful.

480
00:29:43,281 --> 00:29:45,909
Dad, just make sure, okay?

481
00:29:46,743 --> 00:29:48,536
I don't want to lose you.

482
00:29:51,247 --> 00:29:52,624
I promise you, Sofia.

483
00:29:53,500 --> 00:29:54,793
I'll be careful.

484
00:29:56,628 --> 00:29:57,670
Cairo…

485
00:29:58,671 --> 00:30:00,673
you take charge here.

486
00:30:01,382 --> 00:30:02,425
Keep them all safe.

487
00:30:23,446 --> 00:30:24,989
Here. Let's stay here first.

488
00:30:26,366 --> 00:30:27,325
Rico, check it out.

489
00:30:27,408 --> 00:30:28,910
- Check the room.
- Mother, the baby.

490
00:30:28,993 --> 00:30:30,620
Come in, quick.

491
00:30:34,332 --> 00:30:36,084
What happened? Why?

492
00:30:36,167 --> 00:30:37,043
- Why?
- Son.

493
00:30:37,126 --> 00:30:39,254
Maybe he's hungry.

494
00:30:40,755 --> 00:30:43,466
Sam, is he okay?

495
00:30:45,927 --> 00:30:47,262
I'll just breastfeed him, Mother.

496
00:30:47,345 --> 00:30:48,388
Okay.

497
00:31:11,995 --> 00:31:13,204
So, what now?

498
00:31:14,247 --> 00:31:16,583
Are we trapping ourselves here?

499
00:31:16,666 --> 00:31:18,167
Can't we even go out?

500
00:31:18,251 --> 00:31:21,754
Isn't it dangerous?
Amando is still outside.

501
00:31:21,838 --> 00:31:25,049
And how are you sure
we're safe here, Mercy?

502
00:31:25,133 --> 00:31:27,552
I've locked all
the windows and doors, Ma'am.

503
00:31:27,635 --> 00:31:30,346
So, we'll just wait for someone
to rescue us?

504
00:31:30,430 --> 00:31:34,767
Or some… or some sort
of divine intervention, right?

505
00:31:34,851 --> 00:31:38,354
You, Jericho. God, you're a soldier.

506
00:31:38,438 --> 00:31:40,982
Can't you even protect us?

507
00:31:41,065 --> 00:31:42,817
Please, don't be noisy.

508
00:31:42,901 --> 00:31:44,903
No. You shut up, Mercy.

509
00:31:46,446 --> 00:31:49,449
This is my house.
I can do whatever I want.

510
00:31:50,033 --> 00:31:53,286
You can do whatever you want,
then you go out.

511
00:31:53,369 --> 00:31:56,581
You can make noise there.
Don't bother us here.

512
00:31:57,248 --> 00:31:58,875
Why are you so eager to go out?

513
00:32:10,178 --> 00:32:11,596
Someone is knocking on the door.

514
00:32:15,016 --> 00:32:17,018
Cairo, open the door. Please.

515
00:32:17,101 --> 00:32:18,686
Cairo, don't.

516
00:32:18,770 --> 00:32:20,271
Why?

517
00:32:20,980 --> 00:32:22,899
Maybe it's the Palacios killer.

518
00:32:22,982 --> 00:32:24,484
What if it's Dad?

519
00:32:25,151 --> 00:32:27,403
You're worried about Amando.

520
00:32:27,487 --> 00:32:30,198
You want to make sure
you didn't shoot him seriously.

521
00:32:30,865 --> 00:32:35,745
Or, do you want him gone before
he reveals all about your conspiracy?

522
00:32:35,828 --> 00:32:37,747
For the nth time, Mercy,

523
00:32:37,830 --> 00:32:41,960
I am not, in any way,
in cahoots with that killer.

524
00:32:42,043 --> 00:32:43,544
I'm not his accomplice.

525
00:32:43,628 --> 00:32:45,672
No one believes you.

526
00:32:45,755 --> 00:32:47,507
I'm telling the truth.

527
00:32:48,466 --> 00:32:51,135
I don't care if you believe me or not.

528
00:32:51,219 --> 00:32:52,971
Please, can you just stop?

529
00:32:58,768 --> 00:33:00,687
What if it's Sir Amando?

530
00:33:02,105 --> 00:33:05,274
Mrs. George Palacios,
Sir Galvan, this is Sergeant Tupaz.

531
00:33:06,109 --> 00:33:07,652
Sergeant Tupaz, he said.

532
00:33:08,152 --> 00:33:09,654
Open the door, quick.

533
00:33:13,950 --> 00:33:14,784
Yes, Sarge.

534
00:33:15,368 --> 00:33:18,079
Sir Galvan's family is here.
They seem okay.

535
00:33:19,497 --> 00:33:22,166
Are you the only ones?
What about Sergeant Royales?

536
00:33:22,250 --> 00:33:25,545
He's going to the other house.
He'll check on the people there.

537
00:33:27,130 --> 00:33:28,548
George…

538
00:33:29,173 --> 00:33:31,801
Call Sam. Tell her the police are here.

539
00:33:31,884 --> 00:33:34,220
Okay, I'll try again.

540
00:33:35,596 --> 00:33:38,474
Sam… Sam, are you there?

541
00:33:40,018 --> 00:33:43,062
We're safe, Sam. Sergeant Tupaz is here.

542
00:33:43,146 --> 00:33:45,982
How are you doing over there?
Have you seen Sergeant Royales?

543
00:33:46,065 --> 00:33:47,025
Sam?

544
00:33:49,235 --> 00:33:50,778
Oh, no. Why is no one answering?

545
00:33:51,738 --> 00:33:52,989
My God, my God…

546
00:33:53,072 --> 00:33:56,242
Save us from Amando, my God.

547
00:33:57,618 --> 00:34:01,456
When did you have the right
to shout in my house, Jericho?

548
00:34:02,123 --> 00:34:05,877
Aunt Aurora, our lives are in danger,
and you keep on shouting.

549
00:34:06,586 --> 00:34:10,256
What if Sir Amando came back
and heard your fights?

550
00:34:10,339 --> 00:34:12,300
He would know where we are hiding.

551
00:34:12,884 --> 00:34:14,343
Jericho is right.

552
00:34:15,762 --> 00:34:17,555
Let's all be quiet for now.

553
00:34:22,143 --> 00:34:24,187
Sam, are you there?

554
00:34:25,521 --> 00:34:27,857
George, what's going on with them?

555
00:34:28,483 --> 00:34:31,319
Sergeant Tupaz, what did
Sergeant Royales say?

556
00:34:31,402 --> 00:34:34,697
Sergeant Royales.
Sergeant Royales, update?

557
00:34:36,157 --> 00:34:37,575
<i>All guards down.</i>

558
00:34:37,658 --> 00:34:40,161
<i>Just stay there and secure everyone.</i>

559
00:34:40,870 --> 00:34:41,788
Ten-four.

560
00:34:42,413 --> 00:34:45,333
Daddy. We should have never let him out.

561
00:34:45,416 --> 00:34:48,002
Cairo, can you follow Dad?

562
00:34:48,836 --> 00:34:52,298
Sofia, can't you see
what happened to my neck?

563
00:34:52,799 --> 00:34:55,093
Sir Amando almost slashed me.

564
00:34:55,676 --> 00:34:57,637
You're such a coward, Cairo.

565
00:34:58,137 --> 00:35:00,598
If you don't want to, I'll go.

566
00:35:01,182 --> 00:35:02,391
I'll come with you.

567
00:35:44,058 --> 00:35:45,476
I'm sorry, Son.

568
00:35:47,186 --> 00:35:50,356
I didn't have the courage
to introduce myself to you.

569
00:35:51,482 --> 00:35:53,151
I was a coward.

570
00:35:54,527 --> 00:35:57,822
I was subservient to your mother's wishes.

571
00:36:00,199 --> 00:36:01,659
I got scared

572
00:36:02,660 --> 00:36:04,620
that she would separate us.

573
00:36:08,207 --> 00:36:09,167
Amando,

574
00:36:10,501 --> 00:36:12,461
what happened to us before

575
00:36:13,546 --> 00:36:15,047
was just once.

576
00:36:15,131 --> 00:36:19,468
It will never happen again.

577
00:36:20,094 --> 00:36:21,429
I was drunk then.

578
00:36:21,512 --> 00:36:23,472
I was lonely.

579
00:36:23,556 --> 00:36:25,349
That's why it happened.

580
00:36:26,434 --> 00:36:29,020
But, it will never happen again.

581
00:36:30,313 --> 00:36:32,064
Get that into your head.

582
00:36:36,694 --> 00:36:39,280
Know your place in this house, Amando.

583
00:36:39,363 --> 00:36:40,948
You are just my servant.

584
00:36:41,032 --> 00:36:46,329
You have no right to comment
on my personal affairs.

585
00:36:46,412 --> 00:36:47,246
Now get out.

586
00:36:47,330 --> 00:36:48,998
Amando…

587
00:36:50,666 --> 00:36:54,295
Not all the people we love
will love us back.

588
00:36:57,340 --> 00:37:00,092
I trust you with my life.

589
00:37:02,595 --> 00:37:06,349
I feel safe and protected
when I'm with you.

590
00:37:08,434 --> 00:37:12,104
But, that's all.

591
00:37:13,773 --> 00:37:17,068
- I loved you, Aurora.
- Yes, Amando.

592
00:37:17,568 --> 00:37:20,905
But, you knew I could never love you.

593
00:37:22,031 --> 00:37:24,450
I'm a Palacios and you,

594
00:37:24,951 --> 00:37:27,828
you said it yourself.

595
00:37:28,579 --> 00:37:30,331
you're just a lowly servant.

596
00:38:04,490 --> 00:38:07,285
Thank God. Thank God you're okay.

597
00:38:07,368 --> 00:38:08,536
NEXT EPISODE

598
00:38:08,619 --> 00:38:12,665
Sir, what are the Palacioses plans
for the victims of this massacre?

599
00:38:12,748 --> 00:38:15,334
We will make sure that

600
00:38:16,294 --> 00:38:17,795
the man behind the killings,

601
00:38:18,504 --> 00:38:22,717
<i>the butler the Palacioses have entrusted</i>
<i>with their lives, will not escape justice.</i>

602
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:24,510
Code red.

603
00:38:24,593 --> 00:38:26,262
Immediate change of plan.

604
00:38:26,345 --> 00:38:27,638
We're going to the Palacioses.

605
00:38:28,306 --> 00:38:33,102
They all believe
that Amando is the mastermind.

606
00:38:34,437 --> 00:38:35,855
You know, George,

607
00:38:36,689 --> 00:38:38,858
this is not the ending I dreamed of.
